data.name: AdvancedLabel5.Text
data.value:
*Wii Remote Emulation modes don't support infrared pointing or motion detection.
**The force options should only be used if your game doesn't detect your controller mode properly. (For example, Resident Evil 4 Wii Edition supports the Classic Controller, but it won't work without being patched) **When using the force options, Wii Retail Injections will be patched automatically. For vWii NAND Titles, you may also need to patch your WAD before installing it to NAND:
